Delivering More With Parcel Pending By Quadient

Quadient is the global leader in smart locker solutions for residential, retail, carrier, commercial, and university clients. With nearly 75 million packages delivered through Parcel Pending by Quadient lockers annually, Quadients fast-growing global locker network delivers a safe, secure, and on-demand experience for parcel deliveries and returns.

We are committed to delivering more for our clients, so you can deliver more for your customers. Thats why millions of users rely on our vertical-, location-, and carrier-agnostic parcel locker solutions. Our parcel locker network now encompasses nearly 18,000 locations around the world, with new units being deployed across North America, Europe, and Japan.

Manage More Deliveries to More Places with our Open Locker Network

Todays consumers expect and often demand convenient options for deliveries and returns. Now, carriers and retailers are facing mounting pressure to scale to meet this demand, as well as the rising costs and environmental impact associated with these initiatives.

Our fast-growing, Open Locker Network lets you streamline business operations by facilitating parcel collections and returns to convenient, centralized locker locations. Ready to learn MORE about joining our Open Locker Network?
